                     <interp inst="t17750218-3-off9" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a hempen sack, value one shilling, a bushel and a half of oats in the chaff and beans, value three shillings, and two bushels of barley in the chaff, value four shillings
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17750218-3-victim89" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Deal
                  <interp inst="t17750218-3-victim89" type="surname" value="Deal"></interp>
